transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, thanks for calling Viagra. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, this is Doug Queen. I ordered some Scor-Bru, the A-G-V Pfizer pills.

Speaker 1: And they sent me just regular generic pills.

Speaker 2: Do you have those? You said Doug Queen?

Speaker 1: What's that?

Speaker 2: Oh, you said your name was Doug Queen?

Speaker 1: Yes, yes.

Speaker 2: Are you at 9419 North Broken Bow?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, Mr. Queen, I'm really sorry about that. Do you have those pills there in front of you?

Speaker 1: Yes, I do.

Speaker 2: Would you mind taking one of those pills out of the bottle and let me know what the markings on both sides say, please?

Speaker 1: There's nothing on one side.

Speaker 2: I think it says, I can't hardly read it, A-C-N-3-3.

Speaker 1: So, no, that tells me all I need to know there, Mr. Queen. So you did get the incorrect thing.

Speaker 2: That's a very similar generic to the ones that guys get at the VA.

Speaker 1: We do still sell those. Those are generic Viagra. I mean, you can take it if you want, but it's not the A-G-V you ordered.

Speaker 2: I'm really sorry about that. Thank you for bringing this to our attention, first and foremost.

Speaker 1: What I'm going to do for you, of course, I'm going to send you out a replacement order today.

Speaker 2: It looks like there was just a little glitch in your order. A few of these, like the machines, have just filled them incorrectly.

Speaker 1: So what I'm going to do for you, of course, I'm going to send you out a replacement order today.

Speaker 2: You'll see that come by in the next few days, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: The pills that you have there, they are still generic Viagra. I mean, you can take them if you want.

Speaker 1: You can toss them if you want. You don't have to send them back.

Speaker 2: But I'll send you these new pills either way, okay?

Speaker 1: Yeah, they don't work for me very good, so that's why I wanted to try the new ones.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so I'll send these out to you, and we'll get this taken care of for you really quickly.

Speaker 1: You'll see them come out in the next few days.

Speaker 2: They'll have different markings on the pills. That's how you'll know they're different, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Appreciate it.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
